name: Conflux Machines #02
description: An abstract piece consisting of one of my Manila cityscape photographs duplicated four times and arranged radially in a square. The centerpiece was created by 9 instances of the Content Aware fill function with blend mode set to Lighten, and 1 instance at the topmost layer set to Darken.. By Lucius Felimus: https://www.luciusfelimus.com/
